12:23.680 --> 12:26.560
You have to Dedicate yourself completely to me,

12:26.565 --> 12:28.725
not to Sahaja Yoga, but to me.

12:29.155 --> 12:31.695
Sahaja Yoga is just one of my aspects.

12:32.025 --> 12:34.815
Leaving everything, you have to dedicate.

12:34.865 --> 12:36.525
Complete dedication,

12:36.525 --> 12:39.365
otherwise you cannot ascend any further.

12:39.365 --> 12:41.295
Without questioning, without arguing.

12:41.680 --> 12:46.040
Dedication is the easiest way to get rid of all your angularities,

12:46.620 --> 12:49.120
all your problems, all your badhas.

12:49.680 --> 12:53.440
Complete dedication, is the only way you can grow further.

12:54.020 --> 12:55.120
Krishna said,

12:55.380 --> 12:59.060
‘Sarva dharmanam parityajya, mamekam sharanam vraja’.

12:59.540 --> 13:01.460
Forget all the religion of the world (dharma).

13:01.860 --> 13:04.240
There is no difference between him and me

13:04.240 --> 13:06.220
but today I am the one,

13:06.720 --> 13:09.120
I am the one who has given you Realization.

13:09.880 --> 13:12.780
All these dharmas are to be given up entirely,

13:13.345 --> 13:16.165
and you have to surrender fully from your heart.

13:16.535 --> 13:19.135
Here, as you are before me today,

13:19.135 --> 13:21.335
I want to tell you very frankly,

13:21.745 --> 13:24.335
as Krishna had told only Arjuna,

13:24.335 --> 13:27.435
‘Sarva dharmanam parityajya, mamekam sharanam vraja’.

13:27.740 --> 13:29.300
Shri Krishna has said,

13:29.540 --> 13:32.800
"Give up all your dharmas and surrender them to me,

13:32.800 --> 13:34.100
surrender to my dharma only."

13:34.240 --> 13:36.860
"You should only know what you owe to me."

13:36.860 --> 13:38.600
meaning the Divinity.

13:38.600 --> 13:42.040
Now Shri Krishna is not there, it’s me who is Shri Krishna,

13:42.100 --> 13:44.740
so you must know what you owe to Me.

13:46.640 --> 13:48.800
She can be achieved through bhakti.

13:49.300 --> 13:51.960
She can only be achieved through dedication.

13:52.905 --> 13:55.855
She’s only fond of her bhaktas, the devotees.

13:56.435 --> 13:59.545
For this, meditation is the only way I should say.

13:59.805 --> 14:02.955
Emotionally you may feel closer to me in your heart.

14:03.280 --> 14:06.260
But through meditation, surrender.

14:06.720 --> 14:10.520
Meditation is nothing but surrendering, is complete surrendering.

14:11.200 --> 14:15.180
In your full freedom, complete freedom, you have to surrender.

14:16.740 --> 14:18.240
And only through your bhakti,

14:18.340 --> 14:20.080
through your devotion and dedication,

14:20.080 --> 14:21.560
you can achieve me.

14:21.980 --> 14:26.000
My achievement is the complete manifestation of your Divine powers.

14:29.180 --> 14:32.880
It’s very simple, made so simple.

14:33.940 --> 14:36.680
I’m only pleased by people who are simple,

14:36.800 --> 14:38.940
innocent, who are not tricky,

14:39.480 --> 14:42.160
who are loving, affectionate to each other.

14:42.540 --> 14:44.400
It’s very easy to please me.

14:44.920 --> 14:47.080
When I see you loving each other,

14:47.500 --> 14:51.540
talking good of each other, helping each other, respecting each other,

14:51.980 --> 14:55.960
laughing aloud together, enjoying together each other’s company,

14:56.680 --> 14:58.900
I get my blessing, my first joy.

15:00.480 --> 15:02.500
So, the dedication in meditation,

15:03.640 --> 15:06.780
complete dedication in meditation, must be practiced.

15:07.580 --> 15:11.780
It’s not for your good now you are doing it, so-called ‘your’.

15:12.060 --> 15:14.200
First you were a little baby, a small thing;

15:15.060 --> 15:17.680
now you are that collective being,

15:17.800 --> 15:21.500
you are not doing anything for yourself, but for that collective being.

15:22.400 --> 15:24.620
You are growing to be aware of that whole

15:24.900 --> 15:26.680
which you are going to become.

15:27.100 --> 15:30.000
Your jobs, your money, your wives,

15:30.300 --> 15:33.600
your husbands, your children, your father, mother, relations,

15:33.660 --> 15:36.280
these considerations are over now.

15:36.500 --> 15:40.660
You all have to take up the responsibility of Sahaja Yoga.

15:41.120 --> 15:43.660
Every one of you is quite capable.

15:44.900 --> 15:46.640
You are brought up for that.

15:47.000 --> 15:50.400
In dedication, in complete devotion, you have to do it

15:50.720 --> 15:54.315
now, not for your own gain, for your own achievement,

15:54.320 --> 15:55.980
that is over now.

15:56.340 --> 15:58.860
It’s for completely getting out of the mire

15:58.980 --> 16:04.600
and standing on the land, singing aloud the praise of your Father.

16:04.600 --> 16:06.740
You have to bear the brunt,

16:06.820 --> 16:08.560
and the sacrifice,

16:09.020 --> 16:11.060
which are no more sacrifices to you

16:11.060 --> 16:13.720
because Spirit gives, it never sacrifices.

16:14.820 --> 16:19.740
Its quality is to give. So, you don’t sacrifice, you just give.

16:20.540 --> 16:22.680
Today, one more lecture Mother?

16:22.680 --> 16:24.680
Yes, yes. It's coming out well.

16:26.720 --> 16:28.200
Our greatest possession.

16:28.600 --> 16:31.540
The greatest possession you have is your Mother.

16:32.615 --> 16:35.485
Through her you have your brothers and sisters.

16:36.235 --> 16:38.945
Now the name of your Mother is very powerful.

16:39.460 --> 16:43.460
You know that is the most powerful name than all other names,

16:44.060 --> 16:47.460
the most powerful name. But you must know how to take it.

16:49.880 --> 16:53.000
With that complete dedication you have to take that name.

16:53.220 --> 16:57.460
I have taken birth in this world in the binding of Sahaja Yogis

16:58.040 --> 17:01.440
and have been moving around only in their binding.

17:02.220 --> 17:04.240
I am desireless

17:04.240 --> 17:07.540
and hence my everything depends upon your desires.

17:07.780 --> 17:11.520
Attain Me; I am yours! I am for you.

17:12.340 --> 17:17.240
I have given you that which has been beyond the reach of very great sages and saints.

17:17.880 --> 17:22.760
When I’m speaking it is a mantra, when I’m not speaking, is a mantra flowing.

17:23.860 --> 17:28.100
Those who are fanatically adhering to me are also not correct.

17:28.780 --> 17:31.140
There should be no fanaticism about it.

17:31.140 --> 17:33.260
But the ideal one important thing.

