18:37.300 --> 18:39.820
The person who is peaceful is powerful

18:40.260 --> 18:44.440
the one who doesn’t react to anything else, is the most powerful.

18:45.160 --> 18:47.700
You have to be kind to others.

18:48.760 --> 18:50.520
You have to be neat and clean.

18:50.820 --> 18:55.660
First is forgiveness, second the detachment leading to compassion.

18:56.280 --> 18:59.860
These are the wheels of your chariot which moves you.

19:01.080 --> 19:04.920
You have been made like temples. Keep it clean.

19:05.480 --> 19:09.180
We are moving towards the soothing qualities of the Spirit.

19:09.860 --> 19:13.800
You have to ‘soothe’ the others and not to excite, but to soothe.

19:14.600 --> 19:18.100
Let God’s melodies be sounded from your flutes.

19:18.820 --> 19:22.540
You must have the capacity to deepen your meditative power,

19:22.860 --> 19:26.360
so that these ideals go and settle in your heart,

19:26.360 --> 19:29.040
as a part and parcel of your being.

19:29.600 --> 19:34.480
Once the saints know this is the principle on which we have to live,

19:34.480 --> 19:36.580
they become one with the principles.

19:37.520 --> 19:38.700


19:39.580 --> 19:43.780
these are principles on which we have to live are there.

19:44.180 --> 19:46.460
You become the mother,

19:46.460 --> 19:50.800
and you, whatever you are which has to grow, is the child.

19:52.480 --> 19:55.980
If you are a Sahaja Yogi you have to be a flower,

19:56.120 --> 19:59.860
and a strong flower, and an eternal flower

19:59.860 --> 20:03.280
that always grows, does not fade out,

20:03.280 --> 20:05.760
always growing, never fades,

20:05.760 --> 20:07.560
such a flower you have to be.

20:08.460 --> 20:11.640
Sahaja Yogis should never be angry.

20:12.760 --> 20:15.480


20:16.360 --> 20:18.260
If somebody has to tell you

20:18.780 --> 20:20.700
that you must organize go fast

20:21.380 --> 20:24.180
and hold back and do not feel bad.

20:24.180 --> 20:26.555
We have to do so much work in this world.

20:26.560 --> 20:28.600
We have no time to waste.

20:29.060 --> 20:32.080
Truly keep the maryadas in Sahaja Yoga

20:32.080 --> 20:37.220
same morning and evening that, "I am a Sahaja Yogi", nobody can harm you,

20:38.340 --> 20:41.020
hurt you, nobody can trouble you.

20:41.435 --> 20:43.140
On the contrary,

20:43.140 --> 20:44.845
you will be enjoying life

20:44.925 --> 20:46.695
if you keep to the maryadas.

20:47.785 --> 20:49.815
One must promise to God that,

20:50.280 --> 20:52.560
"We’ll know about Sahaja Yoga

20:52.980 --> 20:54.680
through proper understanding

20:55.180 --> 20:56.840
reading every word of it.

20:57.525 --> 20:59.965
We’ll master the knowledge of Sahaja Yoga.

21:00.495 --> 21:02.385
We will keep ourselves clean

21:02.780 --> 21:06.640
and completely surrender ourselves, our lives to Sahaja Yoga."

21:07.300 --> 21:11.240
Surrendering to Sahaja Yoga is actually surrendering to joy,

21:11.760 --> 21:13.320
bliss and peace.

21:14.735 --> 21:16.605
Language should be sweet.

21:16.965 --> 21:18.815
Your behaviour should be good.

21:19.295 --> 21:21.145
You should be very gentle and soft;

21:21.700 --> 21:25.200
you should move like a Yogi, live like a saint.

21:25.780 --> 21:28.220
And people should see through you

21:28.220 --> 21:30.060
the greatness of Sahaja Yoga.

21:30.900 --> 21:32.480
See the trees

21:32.580 --> 21:36.420
when they get their flowers, they are not so respectful.

21:36.960 --> 21:39.980
But when they are laden by the fruits

21:39.980 --> 21:41.860
they bow down to Mother Earth.

21:41.860 --> 21:43.460
In the same way

21:43.680 --> 21:46.000
when you have got the fruits of Sahaja Yoga,

21:46.000 --> 21:48.000
you all must bow down.

21:48.600 --> 21:50.600
You have to be sensitive to God

21:50.780 --> 21:52.960
and not to bad things.

21:53.240 --> 21:56.340
You have to change your methods.

21:56.340 --> 21:58.740
The person who cannot change his methods

21:58.740 --> 22:00.540
cannot spread Sahaja Yoga.

22:00.840 --> 22:03.740
Because he sticks to only to one way.

22:03.880 --> 22:05.740
with which people get bored.

22:06.045 --> 22:07.595
You should find new ways.

22:08.480 --> 22:10.720
An established Sahaja Yogi is the one

22:11.180 --> 22:13.840
who becomes completely one with God

22:13.960 --> 22:15.800
and wins him over.

22:16.260 --> 22:17.940
He has to do everything for that.

22:17.940 --> 22:20.140
This is how is a true Sahaja Yogi.

