How to keep Mother pleased.

22:33.480 --> 22:37.000
That’s me, so that I know!

22:39.100 --> 22:41.680
So, how to please Mother?

22:42.420 --> 22:44.640
I am also a simple person

22:45.100 --> 22:48.500
so I want a simple-hearted person.

22:49.900 --> 22:52.180


22:53.720 --> 22:57.000
So, this Heart Chakra is to be first looked after.

22:57.720 --> 23:01.520
That with your heart - desire, you will keep your Mother pleased.

23:05.800 --> 23:08.335
First of all, your heart must be clear.

23:08.335 --> 23:10.145
If the heart is not clear,

23:10.145 --> 23:13.880
then everything has no meaning because it is a “dark heart”

23:14.580 --> 23:17.400
which is doing all these things.

23:17.500 --> 23:20.260
The heart has to be clean, absolutely surrendered

23:20.720 --> 23:23.820
and must try to put me before everything else.

23:24.520 --> 23:28.360
The Lakshmi tattva has to become Mahalakshmi tattva.

23:29.100 --> 23:31.140
That is for your ascent.

23:32.000 --> 23:36.100
And just to get into the Mahalakshmi tattva

23:36.940 --> 23:40.460
what you have to do is to use all your material things

23:41.180 --> 23:43.740
and your material being in such a way

23:43.880 --> 23:45.640
that you please me.

23:46.280 --> 23:48.720
Bapre, give me horrible things, all right.

23:48.720 --> 23:50.700
You have to keep your Mother pleased

23:50.800 --> 23:53.300
You have to keep your Mother pleased by pleasing other Sahaja Yogis

23:54.020 --> 23:55.620
and not other people.

23:57.100 --> 24:01.440
What guru dakshinat have you given me?

24:01.920 --> 24:06.960
Understand that your money is not worth the dust

24:06.960 --> 24:10.140
on the feet of your Mother Guru.

24:11.340 --> 24:13.160
You should give your hearts,

24:13.580 --> 24:16.200
only clean and holy hearts.

24:17.380 --> 24:19.520
You must clean your physical beings.

24:20.480 --> 24:23.420
You must get up early in the morning

24:23.420 --> 24:26.640
and spend at least one hour on meditation and worshipping.

24:26.985 --> 24:30.015
Perform "Aarti" and meditation in the evening.

24:34.000 --> 24:36.000
I'll read about laws of the Divine.

24:36.960 --> 24:38.980
One must know

24:39.580 --> 24:41.220
these laws of the Divine,

24:42.000 --> 24:44.880
that you have to live with self-respect

24:45.215 --> 24:46.865
that we have to be chaste.

24:47.725 --> 24:49.585
that we have to have dignity,

24:50.155 --> 24:53.375
that we cannot steal money and steal things

24:54.060 --> 24:56.300
and be parasites.

24:57.200 --> 24:59.020
That we cannot kill others

24:59.660 --> 25:01.200
and we cannot beat others

25:01.680 --> 25:03.220
and say harsh things,

25:03.820 --> 25:05.360
they are just the same.

25:06.220 --> 25:09.340
And that we have respect,

25:09.340 --> 25:12.340
the respect for all that is sublime.

25:13.240 --> 25:15.160
Respect for all the saints

25:16.000 --> 25:17.920
that are Sahaja Yogis.

25:17.920 --> 25:21.340
And the respect for the leaders who represent you Mother.

25:21.980 --> 25:25.000
With all this, we are very different people.

25:25.380 --> 25:26.660
We are different race.

25:26.960 --> 25:28.600
We are virtuous,

25:28.840 --> 25:29.960
we are righteous

25:30.280 --> 25:32.280
and we are proud to be that way.

25:32.680 --> 25:34.400
We are sure of everything.

25:34.440 --> 25:36.440
We know about every thing.

25:36.840 --> 25:38.840
And we are personification of Compassion,

25:39.100 --> 25:40.600
of Love of God.

25:40.600 --> 25:42.460
That’s what we are.

25:42.460 --> 25:44.680
We are not ordinary people.

25:45.140 --> 25:48.080
On the subtler side is compassion is forgiveness

25:48.300 --> 25:49.580
is love.

25:50.405 --> 25:53.385
But the greatest of all is service to God.

25:53.615 --> 25:55.405
We are doing the work of God.

25:55.825 --> 25:57.325
How can we be tired?

